WEBVTT

01:27.370 --> 01:31.910
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.250 --> 01:34.920
[Episode 19]

01:41.870 --> 01:42.870
Off to Jinfangdi!

01:42.960 --> 01:45.009
[Harbor Island]

01:44.000 --> 01:44.600
Over here!

01:46.280 --> 01:46.840
This bus!

01:48.229 --> 01:50.229
Setting off in 10 minutes. Get on the bus.

01:50.229 --> 01:53.600
[Tongwan to Jinfangdi]

01:50.950 --> 01:51.590
Over here!

01:53.070 --> 01:54.430
This bus is off to Jinfangdi.

01:54.430 --> 01:55.280
Hop on!

01:58.640 --> 01:59.479
Get on the bus!

02:00.760 --> 02:01.430
Right here!

02:02.050 --> 02:06.390
[Harbor Island Edward Hospital]

02:06.150 --> 02:07.400
That fire

02:07.400 --> 02:08.800
was a serious incident.

02:09.430 --> 02:10.490
It's known to many.

02:12.150 --> 02:13.840
The doctor on duty was...

02:14.680 --> 02:17.240
Dr. Tao, as I remember.

02:18.000 --> 02:19.000
After the incident,

02:19.000 --> 02:20.860
he was dismissed by the hospital.

02:25.300 --> 02:27.430
This is the news report about the fire.

02:27.470 --> 02:28.530
You can take a look.

02:29.100 --> 02:32.460
[Psychiatric patient goes crazy
and sets a fire]

02:30.240 --> 02:31.240
One dead, two injured.

02:31.240 --> 02:32.360
Serious, indeed.

02:32.480 --> 02:35.230
[One dead and two injured
in Edward Hospital]

02:35.900 --> 02:37.300
"Dr. Tao"?

02:38.079 --> 02:38.560
Yes.

02:39.280 --> 02:41.240
It was Dr. Tao, Tao Jiajun.

02:42.430 --> 02:43.470
"T-Tao..."

02:43.470 --> 02:44.400
What's his name?

02:44.870 --> 02:45.910
"Tao Jiajun."

02:48.550 --> 02:50.680
Did you come here
to ask about this matter?

02:50.680 --> 02:51.150
Yes.

03:11.150 --> 03:11.880
Hey, Dr. Tao.

03:12.600 --> 03:15.200
I-I couldn't find No. 491.

03:15.400 --> 03:16.870
I walked past No. 489, and there was

03:16.870 --> 03:18.240
no other building ahead.

03:18.240 --> 03:19.240
Where are you now?

03:20.100 --> 03:21.350
I'm in a plaza.

03:21.800 --> 03:23.030
There are many people.

03:23.030 --> 03:23.960
Over here! Here!

03:24.280 --> 03:25.310
Yes, I'm in a blue jacket.

03:25.310 --> 03:26.510
I'm right behind you!

03:26.960 --> 03:27.760
Can you see me?

03:31.680 --> 03:32.150
Dr. Tao.

03:32.270 --> 03:33.000
Hello, Li.

03:33.000 --> 03:33.280
I'm Li.

03:33.280 --> 03:34.000
Yes, I am.

03:34.680 --> 03:36.470
The incident ruined

03:36.750 --> 03:38.410
my professional reputation.

03:38.750 --> 03:40.240
It took a toll on my career,

03:40.240 --> 03:42.170
and I couldn't be a doctor anymore.

03:42.560 --> 03:44.360
Would you like to buy insurance?

03:44.360 --> 03:44.970
No, no.

03:45.120 --> 03:46.130
Dr. Tao,

03:46.400 --> 03:47.750
my mother manages all my money.

03:47.750 --> 03:49.280
I can't make any decisions.

03:49.800 --> 03:50.280
Dr. Tao,

03:50.680 --> 03:53.520
that woman, Qiao Lihua,
who set the fire years ago,

03:53.750 --> 03:55.410
was a patient of yours, right?

03:56.079 --> 03:58.280
Do you remember her medical condition
at that time?

03:58.280 --> 03:59.730
Back then, she just

04:00.080 --> 04:01.940
had some trouble falling asleep.

04:02.080 --> 04:03.710
It was insomnia and stuff.

04:04.150 --> 04:05.430
Her condition was not serious.

04:05.430 --> 04:06.820
She came to see me to address

04:06.820 --> 04:08.540
her sleeping problems,

04:09.080 --> 04:11.800
so she could have the energy
to work several jobs during the day.

04:11.800 --> 04:12.840
A long time ago,

04:12.840 --> 04:16.160
she married a man from the Harbor Island
and moved here with her daughter

04:16.160 --> 04:17.490
from Tanhua, Nanhu.

04:17.529 --> 04:18.360
Her husband

04:18.510 --> 04:19.190
was old

04:19.480 --> 04:20.269
and lazy.

04:21.269 --> 04:24.200
I knew it was hard for her
to support the family alone.

04:24.270 --> 04:26.390
But we had to follow certain rules
when prescribing medicine.

04:26.390 --> 04:27.830
We couldn't give out too many drugs.

04:27.830 --> 04:29.070
Every time before we prescribed,

04:29.070 --> 04:31.270
we had to charge
registration and consultation fees.

04:31.270 --> 04:32.870
Despite all her discontent,

04:33.480 --> 04:35.010
she had no reason to kill me.

04:36.000 --> 04:37.830
She even b-brought gasoline and a dagger

04:37.830 --> 04:38.830
to the hospital that day.

04:38.830 --> 04:40.560
She must've thought it all out.

04:40.830 --> 04:42.000
I don't know.

04:42.380 --> 04:44.710
Could you describe what exactly happened

04:44.800 --> 04:46.040
that day?

04:46.630 --> 04:48.750
I... don't think I could.

04:49.390 --> 04:50.190
Because I was not there

04:50.190 --> 04:51.520
when the fire happened.

04:51.860 --> 04:52.920
You weren't there?

04:53.070 --> 04:53.870
That day,

04:53.870 --> 04:54.800
my daughter suddenly

04:54.800 --> 04:56.240
had an issue at school.

04:56.240 --> 04:57.830
So I took a leave and went to be with her.

04:57.830 --> 04:58.560
As for what exactly

04:58.560 --> 04:59.800
happened in the hospital,

04:59.800 --> 05:00.950
I have no idea at all.

05:01.680 --> 05:05.140
Only the medical intern I was supervising
back then was there.

05:05.720 --> 05:06.520
Well, then...

05:06.630 --> 05:09.270
The newspaper said the fire
was caused
by a doctor-patient dispute.

05:09.270 --> 05:11.600
That information was actually told
by the intern?

05:11.600 --> 05:12.070
Yes.

05:12.630 --> 05:13.810
Qiao Lihua died.

05:14.070 --> 05:16.160
Her daughter escaped the fire
and went insane.

05:16.160 --> 05:17.830
She just wouldn't say anything.

05:17.830 --> 05:20.190
I heard she was sent
to a psychiatric hospital.

05:20.190 --> 05:21.830
That medical intern

05:21.830 --> 05:23.430
became a hero who saved a life.

05:23.430 --> 05:25.630
People would believe whatever he said.

05:25.830 --> 05:27.920
Do you still remember the name

05:28.350 --> 05:29.210
of that intern?

05:29.750 --> 05:31.600
There's no way I'll ever forget it.

05:31.600 --> 05:32.600
It's "Luo Liang."

05:36.950 --> 05:38.400
Take a seat there.

05:41.830 --> 05:42.350
Sit.

05:48.600 --> 05:51.630
We just came down here
and you're already sweating a lot.

05:51.630 --> 05:53.190
Let me wipe the sweat off.

05:55.430 --> 05:56.360
Are you thirsty?

05:58.480 --> 05:59.730
Just wait here.

06:00.070 --> 06:01.560
I'll go fetch you water.

06:04.800 --> 06:05.860
Don't go anywhere!

06:25.560 --> 06:26.690
Are you feeling hot?

06:30.750 --> 06:32.680
As if you were being burned by fire,

06:33.830 --> 06:34.310
right?

06:49.000 --> 06:50.600
Actually, you love the heat.

06:51.210 --> 06:51.850
I know...

06:52.670 --> 06:54.530
that you enjoy playing with fire,

06:57.630 --> 06:59.490
yet your mother wouldn't let you.

06:59.820 --> 07:01.550
That was why you hated her guts.

07:02.280 --> 07:04.210
So much so that you wanted her dead.

07:14.280 --> 07:15.790
I bet you must be happy now.

07:16.940 --> 07:17.980
You kept thinking

07:18.550 --> 07:20.150
if she was out of the picture,

07:20.230 --> 07:23.240
you could be
with the man you loved forever.

07:24.190 --> 07:27.520
It just didn't occur to you
that she would really disappear.

07:27.610 --> 07:29.340
Nobody could stop you anymore.

07:30.290 --> 07:31.130
God heard

07:31.420 --> 07:32.700
your wish,

07:33.270 --> 07:34.870
and made it come true for you.

07:35.270 --> 07:36.270
Wasn't it great?

07:58.870 --> 08:00.270
You should celebrate it.

08:23.750 --> 08:24.390
Yuan.

08:29.830 --> 08:30.600
Zishan!

08:32.150 --> 08:33.200
Zishan!

08:36.080 --> 08:36.960
Zishan!

08:55.790 --> 08:57.550
I told you not to go anywhere.

08:57.870 --> 08:59.120
I was scared for you.

09:06.240 --> 09:07.170
What's with you?

09:07.530 --> 09:08.860
Are you feeling unwell?

09:12.440 --> 09:13.430
Go to sleep then.

09:34.870 --> 09:36.000
I'm terribly sorry.

09:36.630 --> 09:37.560
We're obligated

09:38.080 --> 09:40.140
to respect every patient's privacy.

09:40.960 --> 09:41.790
Zishan was just

09:41.790 --> 09:42.790
transferred last month.

09:42.790 --> 09:44.590
If only you had come before that.

09:45.450 --> 09:46.790
Could you please tell me

09:46.790 --> 09:48.770
where Qiao Zishan was transferred to?

09:48.770 --> 09:49.730
Morning, sir!

09:50.240 --> 09:50.840
Morning!

09:51.320 --> 09:52.080
Greetings received.

09:52.080 --> 09:53.140
Make way, will you?

09:54.030 --> 09:55.880
You're asking about Zishan...

09:56.780 --> 09:58.380
Did something happen to her?

09:58.790 --> 10:00.310
I remember getting a call

10:00.340 --> 10:02.720
from the Harbor Island police
a few days ago,

10:02.720 --> 10:05.630
saying they were helping the Wuzhou police
in the mainland

10:05.630 --> 10:07.550
to gather information about Zishan.

10:07.550 --> 10:08.420
Wuzhou police?

10:10.370 --> 10:13.210
Isn't Qiao Zishan from Tanhua,
Nanhu Province?

10:13.240 --> 10:16.040
Why are the Wuzhou police
investigating her case?

10:17.030 --> 10:17.550
Sorry.

10:18.840 --> 10:20.000
Without police authorization,

10:20.000 --> 10:20.630
we...

10:20.630 --> 10:22.760
can't disclose too much information.

10:23.550 --> 10:24.080
This way.

10:27.550 --> 10:28.720
My apologies

10:28.840 --> 10:29.870
for not being helpful.

10:29.870 --> 10:30.670
I understand.

10:33.750 --> 10:35.360
This sanatorium has been bought out.

10:35.360 --> 10:37.290
It's under renovation these days,

10:37.430 --> 10:38.830
so things are a bit messy.

10:41.840 --> 10:42.390
Xu!

10:43.150 --> 10:44.200
That's scaffolding.

10:44.200 --> 10:45.460
Don't play over there!

10:47.030 --> 10:48.430
Stop playing over there!

10:52.960 --> 10:54.200
It's dangerous here.

10:54.670 --> 10:55.750
Stick the paper elsewhere.

10:55.750 --> 10:57.670
I'm not finished yet.

10:58.000 --> 10:58.870
Go there. Stick the paper there.

10:58.870 --> 11:01.200
Bring this
and let us take you to eat, okay?

11:01.200 --> 11:01.600
Fang,

11:01.910 --> 11:03.080
have this area blocked off.

11:02.170 --> 11:03.850
[Harbor Island-Style Diner]

11:09.080 --> 11:09.880
Who drew this?

11:29.160 --> 11:29.990
Zishan.

11:33.370 --> 11:34.420
Listen to me.

11:36.150 --> 11:37.990
You must not be with him.

11:38.820 --> 11:40.840
How could a man who has ruined your future

11:40.840 --> 11:42.670
and put you through hell

11:42.670 --> 11:44.870
genuinely love you?

11:46.360 --> 11:47.790
You must not be with him.

11:47.790 --> 11:51.150
You're practically playing with fire.

11:52.440 --> 11:53.150
I have never

11:53.150 --> 11:54.950
loved someone the way I love you.

11:55.270 --> 11:56.560
But your mother said

11:57.200 --> 11:59.580
she would rather die
than let us be together.

11:59.580 --> 12:00.990
How could I bring myself

12:01.440 --> 12:03.370
to really let you hurt your mother?

12:07.600 --> 12:10.170
God heard your wish.

12:10.770 --> 12:12.630
Your mother really disappeared.

12:13.480 --> 12:14.880
You should celebrate it.

12:15.250 --> 12:16.850
You should celebrate it.

12:17.750 --> 12:19.230
You should celebrate it.

12:20.270 --> 12:21.740
You should celebrate it.

13:01.010 --> 13:02.420
[Special Care Unit]

13:01.090 --> 13:02.080
Your fellow Wuzhou police

13:02.080 --> 13:04.200
have also contacted Minkang Sanatorium
on the Harbor Island.

13:02.420 --> 13:03.870
[Wuzhou People's Hospital]

13:04.500 --> 13:07.700
[Special Care Unit]

13:04.550 --> 13:06.600
Yes, Qiao Zishan was getting better.

13:06.600 --> 13:08.030
The fire broke out all of a sudden.

13:08.030 --> 13:10.230
Nobody knows
how she got a fire lighter.

13:10.280 --> 13:11.720
Fortunately, the fire was put out in time.

13:11.720 --> 13:13.320
So she wasn't badly injured.

13:19.870 --> 13:22.530
We're giving her a larger dose
of sedatives now.

13:23.320 --> 13:23.780
Doctor.

13:25.450 --> 13:28.210
Does she have a tattoo in this pattern?

13:29.840 --> 13:31.360
The left side of her body

13:31.440 --> 13:33.700
has large, old burn scars.

13:34.000 --> 13:35.320
As for tattoos...

13:36.390 --> 13:37.550
I think she has one in her lower back.

13:37.550 --> 13:38.150
In this pattern?

13:38.150 --> 13:39.670
But most of it was burned.

13:41.550 --> 13:43.630
This part looks a bit like it, though.

13:44.560 --> 13:45.180
This?

13:46.150 --> 13:47.350
It's confirmed then.

13:47.910 --> 13:49.270
Director Huang of that sanatorium
on the Harbor Island

13:49.270 --> 13:51.200
said this was drawn by Qiao Zishan.

13:52.150 --> 13:54.480
She must've also fallen victim to Mister.

13:56.640 --> 13:58.630
You said she had regained consciousness
for a while.

13:58.630 --> 14:00.240
Is it possible for us
to ask her questions?

14:00.240 --> 14:01.970
Her testimony means a lot to us.

14:03.020 --> 14:04.720
Her consciousness is recovering.

14:04.720 --> 14:07.020
But a tricky situation tends to rise

14:07.670 --> 14:09.270
when you talk to a patient like her.

14:09.270 --> 14:12.000
That is, usually, she feels more reluctant
to speak of things

14:12.000 --> 14:14.460
she'd hate to bring up
when she's conscious.

14:16.720 --> 14:17.720
Unless...

14:18.840 --> 14:19.720
Unless what?

14:20.550 --> 14:20.960
Right.

14:21.510 --> 14:24.630
The doctor said we could consider
putting her under hypnosis.

14:24.630 --> 14:25.160
Captain,

14:25.670 --> 14:26.730
should we go for it?

14:45.480 --> 14:46.610
Breakfast is ready.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.460
I‘m not hungry.

14:50.600 --> 14:51.530
Thanks, though.

15:03.420 --> 15:04.720
[A fire accidentally broke out last night
at Wuzhou People's Hospital]

15:04.740 --> 15:06.570
[It is suspected to be set
by an inpatient]

15:09.410 --> 15:10.150
[Mr. Zhang, a witness]

15:10.170 --> 15:11.030
[who lives near the hospital,]

15:11.050 --> 15:11.790
[said he noticed the hospital was in fire]

15:11.820 --> 15:12.580
[Multiple police cars and fire trucks
arrived at the scene soon]

15:15.260 --> 15:16.110
[Emergency Fire Report]

15:27.560 --> 15:32.110
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

15:38.520 --> 15:42.860
[Remember to eat. I love you]

15:43.000 --> 15:44.070
I couldn't fall sleep.

15:44.070 --> 15:48.150
[I'm very upset]

15:44.550 --> 15:45.350
How about you?

15:47.580 --> 15:49.070
I'm very upset.

15:50.000 --> 15:51.530
Why are we always fighting?

15:53.720 --> 15:55.740
[I couldn't sleep the entire night.
What about you?]

15:54.240 --> 15:55.630
Can we stop fighting?

15:58.730 --> 16:00.820
[I'm very upset.
Why are we always fighting?]

15:59.250 --> 16:00.510
I'm worried about you.

16:01.320 --> 16:03.270
Are you as upset as I am?

16:04.550 --> 16:05.670
It's been hours.

16:07.150 --> 16:08.610
Yet I haven't slept a wink.

16:12.440 --> 16:13.300
Are you asleep?

16:18.320 --> 16:20.450
I really hate to get in a fight with you.

16:23.270 --> 16:23.910
I love you.

16:24.870 --> 16:25.800
Remember to eat.

16:28.510 --> 16:29.480
You're right.

16:28.740 --> 16:32.860
[You're right. My life...]

16:30.010 --> 16:31.170
My life

16:31.270 --> 16:33.840
is indeed
filled with irreparable mistakes.

16:32.900 --> 16:37.270
[My life is indeed
filled with irreparable mistakes]

16:34.270 --> 16:36.480
So I retreated into a protective carapace

16:36.480 --> 16:38.150
and became reliant on only myself.

16:37.320 --> 16:40.610
[So I retreated into a protective carapace
and become reliant on only myself]

16:38.480 --> 16:40.080
I even put on a tough exterior.

16:40.080 --> 16:41.150
But meanwhile,

16:40.660 --> 16:43.720
[I even put on a tough exterior.
But meanwhile, I was weak]

16:41.170 --> 16:42.120
I was weak.

16:42.120 --> 16:43.150
I...

16:43.670 --> 16:45.390
"I think," "I assume," "I remember"...

16:43.750 --> 16:45.300
[I was too weak to face my...]

16:45.910 --> 16:48.750
You passionately confessed your love
for another man

16:48.750 --> 16:50.790
with words of affection
that you have never said to me.

16:50.790 --> 16:52.630
Have you ever taken my feelings
into consideration?

16:52.630 --> 16:54.960
Why can't you care about someone else
than yourself?

16:54.960 --> 16:56.910
I've done everything I can to support you.

16:55.000 --> 16:56.340
[Honey]

16:57.440 --> 16:59.090
How can I accept all this?

16:59.550 --> 17:00.880
I'm so sorry. I'm sorry.

17:00.930 --> 17:02.480
[Honey]

17:01.870 --> 17:02.540
I'm sorry.

17:17.030 --> 17:18.310
I really am so sorry.

17:18.310 --> 17:19.440
It's all my fault.

17:19.550 --> 17:20.550
You should know

17:20.750 --> 17:23.119
that except my father and Jiale,

17:23.310 --> 17:24.589
you are the only man I love in this world.

17:24.589 --> 17:26.240
Dr. Luo, today's meeting
has been rescheduled

17:26.240 --> 17:27.109
for tomorrow.

17:28.329 --> 17:28.810
Really?

17:29.160 --> 17:29.880
What are you laughing at?

17:29.880 --> 17:30.740
You seem happy.

17:32.000 --> 17:32.960
I'm in a great mood.

17:32.960 --> 17:34.220
Because I can rest now.

17:34.880 --> 17:35.750
I'll get back to work then.

17:35.750 --> 17:36.210
Thanks.

17:40.300 --> 17:41.950
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

17:44.670 --> 17:46.790
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

17:59.350 --> 18:00.200
Hey, Honey.

18:00.880 --> 18:01.340
Ms. Yan,

18:02.270 --> 18:03.550
this is Li.

18:05.310 --> 18:06.070
Officer Li,

18:06.920 --> 18:08.050
what can I do for you?

18:08.070 --> 18:10.710
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

18:10.920 --> 18:13.310
Well, is your husband at home?

18:14.160 --> 18:15.200
He's off to work.

18:15.900 --> 18:16.610
Good.

18:18.110 --> 18:21.160
I... need a word with you.

18:27.690 --> 18:30.530
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

18:35.040 --> 18:36.190
[July 17, 2019, Wednesday]

19:00.440 --> 19:00.920
Ms. Yan,

19:03.200 --> 19:05.590
this is head of the Special Crimes Unit,
Wang Haoying,

19:05.590 --> 19:06.390
Officer Wang.

19:08.310 --> 19:09.240
Nice to meet you.

19:12.720 --> 19:13.650
Ms. Yan, when...

19:14.200 --> 19:16.640
did you and Dr. Luo first meet?

19:19.750 --> 19:20.750
About...

19:21.350 --> 19:22.720
six months ago,

19:24.400 --> 19:26.530
around the time of Leilei's incident.

19:29.480 --> 19:33.350
You got married after knowing each other
for only six months?

19:35.570 --> 19:36.770
Did he pursue you?

19:43.890 --> 19:47.370
Why are you guys
suddenly so interested in him?

19:53.310 --> 19:55.840
Do you know
Luo Liang changed his name before?

19:58.310 --> 19:58.880
Yes, I do.

19:59.830 --> 20:00.240
You do?

20:01.110 --> 20:03.030
His former name was Xiao Su.

20:03.830 --> 20:04.850
X-I-A-O, Xiao.

20:05.070 --> 20:05.880
S-U, Su.

20:06.550 --> 20:06.920
Yes.

20:09.200 --> 20:11.160
Do you know why he changed it?

20:14.510 --> 20:15.770
He told me everything.

20:16.590 --> 20:18.790
That was in the past.

20:19.590 --> 20:20.650
I know all about it.

20:23.160 --> 20:23.960
Why?

20:25.480 --> 20:26.540
Is there a problem?

20:33.160 --> 20:34.220
It's our belief...

20:36.920 --> 20:38.380
that he's a dangerous man.

20:39.920 --> 20:40.870
Dangerous?

20:42.200 --> 20:44.000
There's no direct evidence now,

20:44.240 --> 20:45.440
but we do suspect

20:46.440 --> 20:47.240
that Luo Liang

20:48.880 --> 20:51.070
is the true founder
of the PUA Theory that Xia Yi

20:51.070 --> 20:52.200
and others studied.

20:52.310 --> 20:53.270
They call him

20:54.240 --> 20:54.840
"Mister."

20:58.590 --> 21:00.030
[Incoming call: Honey]

21:04.050 --> 21:06.190
[Incoming call: Honey]

21:19.110 --> 21:22.240
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

21:24.350 --> 21:26.220
These are all just speculations

21:26.610 --> 21:27.720
now, right?

21:28.270 --> 21:30.030
You can't prove he is Mister,

21:31.790 --> 21:32.350
can you?

21:36.310 --> 21:36.770
Well...

21:39.960 --> 21:42.030
If he really is Mister,

21:43.770 --> 21:45.700
why would he marry me?

21:52.070 --> 21:55.200
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

22:14.530 --> 22:16.860
I understand why you kept secrets from me.

22:17.430 --> 22:19.230
I've also done a lot of thinking.

22:20.680 --> 22:21.540
No matter what,

22:23.200 --> 22:24.860
I still can't stop loving you.

23:49.310 --> 23:50.310
Did I startle you?

23:51.830 --> 23:53.030
I... I was cooking,

23:53.870 --> 23:55.670
so I didn't notice you were back.

23:58.150 --> 23:58.780
Sorry.

24:00.590 --> 24:03.590
I shouldn't have lost my temper with you
this morning.

24:03.920 --> 24:06.160
You put so much effort
in making breakfast,

24:06.160 --> 24:08.020
yet I left without even eating it.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.280
It's okay.

24:23.650 --> 24:25.250
I was all sulky the whole day,

24:27.400 --> 24:30.000
worrying that you might be upset
at home alone.

24:32.350 --> 24:34.810
I called you
but you didn't answer the phone.

24:35.490 --> 24:36.670
Did you go out?

24:43.750 --> 24:44.880
Yes, for groceries.

24:47.790 --> 24:48.820
Last night,

24:50.160 --> 24:51.690
I forgot to charge my phone.

24:53.980 --> 24:55.780
You only went grocery shopping?

25:10.790 --> 25:11.560
I'm sorry.

25:15.310 --> 25:16.200
I saw the notes

25:16.830 --> 25:18.240
you wrote.

25:19.400 --> 25:21.200
I spent the entire day thinking.

25:23.510 --> 25:24.510
I'm sorry, Honey.

25:27.040 --> 25:27.890
Ding Zhibo...

25:30.060 --> 25:32.130
is like a stinking abscess

25:34.550 --> 25:36.280
that I'd hate to let anyone see.

25:38.240 --> 25:38.790
I was trying

25:38.790 --> 25:42.390
to keep you from thinking
that I still had anything to do with him.

25:42.480 --> 25:43.410
I don't love him.

25:43.880 --> 25:44.680
You know that.

25:48.240 --> 25:49.770
You didn't tell me the truth

25:50.720 --> 25:52.250
because you didn't believe

25:52.790 --> 25:54.750
that I'd trust you and accept you.

25:57.520 --> 25:58.980
In fact, if you had said it,

25:59.480 --> 26:02.480
we could've faced it
and solved the problem together.

26:02.790 --> 26:03.780
Back then,

26:05.750 --> 26:07.490
when that video was released,

26:09.240 --> 26:10.610
didn't you and Lu

26:10.920 --> 26:12.440
report it to Officer Li?

26:17.430 --> 26:18.800
You can ask Officer Li

26:19.400 --> 26:21.240
for help and updates

26:22.000 --> 26:23.200
on Ding Zhibo's case.

26:24.120 --> 26:26.430
He seems like a zealous officer to me.

26:33.080 --> 26:34.080
Attorney Zhou...

26:35.860 --> 26:37.310
previously said

26:37.310 --> 26:40.040
that the p-police had started
an investigation.

26:41.230 --> 26:43.490
She told me to just wait
to hear from them.

26:46.200 --> 26:47.670
Besides, you were right.

26:49.440 --> 26:51.300
I wrote all those letters myself.

26:52.570 --> 26:54.090
It can only prove that I...

27:01.280 --> 27:03.610
I don't want to humiliate myself anymore.

27:36.790 --> 27:37.790
You still have me.

27:55.400 --> 27:56.200
Do you love me?

27:58.310 --> 27:58.860
Yes, I do.

28:02.900 --> 28:06.740
[For Police Officers]
[Notebook]

28:03.400 --> 28:04.750
Read it, Ms. Yan.

28:20.200 --> 28:22.460
[Suicide at Xueyu Royal Hotel]

28:20.270 --> 28:22.260
Now, to our knowledge,

28:24.250 --> 28:25.930
at least 3 girls killed themselves

28:24.480 --> 28:25.580
[Suicide at Xueyu Royal Hotel]

28:25.580 --> 28:27.390
[Tragic! A 22-year-old
former figure skating champion dies]

28:27.030 --> 28:27.960
for Dr. Luo.

28:27.390 --> 28:28.390
[of jumping off a gymnasium]

28:31.510 --> 28:33.480
In addition, the son of one of the victims

28:33.480 --> 28:34.790
clearly remembers this man's name

28:34.790 --> 28:35.650
as "Luo Liang."

28:35.680 --> 28:36.290
Also,

28:36.640 --> 28:37.690
now, a girl...

28:37.720 --> 28:38.880
It's true that we don't have

28:38.880 --> 28:40.270
enough evidence to open a case now,

28:40.270 --> 28:42.480
or treat Luo Liang as a criminal suspect.

28:42.480 --> 28:44.680
But as friends,

28:44.930 --> 28:46.340
we have to warn you.

28:46.510 --> 28:49.200
Being with him now is extremely dangerous.

28:54.520 --> 28:56.580
[Suicide at Xueyu Royal Hotel]

28:59.160 --> 29:00.800
Do you mean...

29:03.270 --> 29:05.880
I'm also his prey?

29:08.550 --> 29:09.950
It's a real possibility.

29:19.790 --> 29:21.880
Then why would he marry me?

29:25.110 --> 29:26.980
That is too high a cost, isn't it?

29:28.000 --> 29:29.100
It depends on...

29:30.160 --> 29:31.680
what he tries to obtain.

29:32.390 --> 29:33.820
What's in it for him?

29:37.610 --> 29:39.740
I'm a single mother

29:40.750 --> 29:42.410
who is close to losing her job.

29:44.250 --> 29:46.780
What do I have that's worth
him doing all that?

29:47.370 --> 29:50.100
Ms. Yan, what's wrong
with being a single mother?

29:50.680 --> 29:52.940
It's not something to be ashamed of.

29:53.800 --> 29:55.310
You can always find a new job.

29:55.310 --> 29:56.200
You are so capable.

29:56.200 --> 29:57.460
What are you afraid of?

30:00.000 --> 30:01.270
Ms. Yan, when I first met you,

30:01.270 --> 30:02.870
you were not like this at all.

30:04.590 --> 30:05.550
You were very brave

30:05.550 --> 30:06.590
and assertive.

30:06.590 --> 30:07.720
Have you forgotten?

30:08.550 --> 30:10.510
If you hadn't insisted
on going after Xia Yi,

30:10.510 --> 30:12.370
I might have been deceived by him.

30:13.510 --> 30:14.720
You're a wonderful woman, Ms. Yan.

30:14.720 --> 30:15.120
You...

30:15.480 --> 30:16.350
You are just great.

30:16.350 --> 30:17.880
Don't sell yourself short.

30:18.920 --> 30:20.750
Do you think Dr. Luo is treating you

30:20.750 --> 30:22.330
differently from his other victims

30:22.330 --> 30:24.370
because you two are married?

30:25.430 --> 30:27.230
But think about this carefully.

30:27.720 --> 30:29.520
Are you happy after meeting him?

30:29.960 --> 30:31.760
Is your life better than before?

30:49.470 --> 30:50.410
I don't know.

30:55.990 --> 30:57.330
Sorry. I'm sorry.

30:58.470 --> 30:59.870
Why are you saying sorry?

31:01.750 --> 31:03.380
I'm sorry. I'm just sorry.

31:05.200 --> 31:07.550
A major characteristic

31:07.550 --> 31:08.680
of gaslighting victims

31:08.680 --> 31:10.200
is that they constantly apologize

31:10.200 --> 31:12.260
and always feel they have done wrong.

31:16.480 --> 31:18.030
Sorry. I'm sorry.

31:23.650 --> 31:25.220
I've lost everything now.

31:26.550 --> 31:27.810
Luo Liang is all I have.

31:29.850 --> 31:31.980
How could he be lying to me?

31:35.310 --> 31:36.310
Ms. Yan, I know...

31:38.350 --> 31:39.720
this is a lot to process.

31:48.310 --> 31:49.170
If

31:50.590 --> 31:52.030
all of this is true,

31:54.000 --> 31:55.730
and he did commit those crimes,

31:59.270 --> 31:59.730
then...

32:00.070 --> 32:01.750
will he be punished?

32:06.790 --> 32:07.750
To be honest,

32:09.960 --> 32:12.270
except for the boy who can prove

32:12.270 --> 32:14.380
that Luo Liang was his tutor,

32:15.070 --> 32:17.720
we have no evidence to prove

32:17.720 --> 32:19.120
that Luo Liang is Mister.

32:20.070 --> 32:22.790
We can't even confirm his identity
at the moment,

32:22.790 --> 32:24.270
let alone prove

32:25.200 --> 32:27.730
that he caused those girls
to commit suicide.

32:35.010 --> 32:37.150
So, did you ask me to come over today

32:38.910 --> 32:41.910
to talk me into leaving him

32:43.220 --> 32:44.320
and divorcing him?

33:11.830 --> 33:12.830
Is it today?

33:17.110 --> 33:18.270
Okay, got it.

33:18.640 --> 33:20.500
Talk to you later in the hospital.

33:23.000 --> 33:23.860
What happened?

33:24.510 --> 33:25.570
I missed a meeting.

33:27.200 --> 33:28.860
I completely forgot about it.

33:30.180 --> 33:31.380
It was all your fault,

33:32.240 --> 33:33.900
for distracting me from work.

33:35.820 --> 33:36.670
I'm sorry.

33:44.880 --> 33:45.400
Honey.

33:46.590 --> 33:48.200
How about I throw that hamster cage away

33:48.200 --> 33:50.110
when I leave for work later?

33:50.400 --> 33:51.720
I'd hate for you to get upset
as you clean it

33:51.720 --> 33:52.720
at home every day.

33:53.200 --> 33:54.550
When Jiale gets in a better mood,

33:54.550 --> 33:56.480
we'll take him to buy a new pet.

33:56.960 --> 33:59.220
Let's wait till we have Jiale's consent.

33:59.800 --> 34:01.730
If we throw the cage away right now,

34:02.110 --> 34:04.170
he'll think that I don't respect him.

34:05.200 --> 34:06.270
By keeping the cage,

34:06.270 --> 34:09.000
I'll have a chance to admit to him
that I did wrong.

34:11.070 --> 34:11.800
That's true.

34:14.360 --> 34:15.670
If you had owned up
to your mistakes earlier,

34:15.670 --> 34:17.730
many things wouldn't have happened.

34:18.360 --> 34:19.090
I'm leaving.

34:23.360 --> 34:24.620
Be careful on the road.

34:24.840 --> 34:25.310
Sure!

34:38.350 --> 34:40.780
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

34:46.670 --> 34:48.830
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

35:07.510 --> 35:10.830
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

35:15.750 --> 35:20.070
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

35:24.760 --> 35:25.470
Honey.

35:25.550 --> 35:27.150
How about I throw that hamster cage away

35:27.150 --> 35:28.950
when I leave for work later?

35:29.510 --> 35:30.800
I'd hate for you to get upset

35:30.800 --> 35:32.600
as you clean it at home every day.

35:47.880 --> 35:51.820
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

35:54.200 --> 35:55.060
Hello, Ms. Yan.

35:55.440 --> 35:55.930
This is

35:56.510 --> 35:57.060
Li.

35:57.550 --> 35:58.480
Officer Li,

35:59.190 --> 36:00.320
what can I do for you?

36:01.190 --> 36:02.710
You can ask Officer Li

36:02.950 --> 36:05.160
for help and updates

36:05.510 --> 36:06.710
on Ding Zhibo's case.

36:07.030 --> 36:09.400
He seems like a zealous officer to me.

36:21.420 --> 36:24.230
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

36:28.770 --> 36:32.940
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

36:37.580 --> 36:42.410
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

36:42.510 --> 36:43.110
Morning, Dr. Luo.

36:43.110 --> 36:44.110
Morning, Dr. Luo.

36:45.510 --> 36:46.730
What's with Dr. Luo today?

36:46.730 --> 36:47.460
I don't know.

36:47.510 --> 36:48.970
He seems to be in a bad mood.

37:06.880 --> 37:10.020
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

37:13.090 --> 37:17.110
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

37:30.710 --> 37:31.500
Dr. Luo,

37:31.600 --> 37:34.260
there are 12 patients
with special needs today.

37:34.630 --> 37:35.030
Okay.

38:07.230 --> 38:10.330
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

38:14.910 --> 38:16.170
Property management?

38:16.550 --> 38:17.190
Hello.

38:17.190 --> 38:18.950
The water is not draining

38:19.700 --> 38:20.900
in my kitchen sink.

38:21.150 --> 38:22.810
I think the pipes are clogged.

38:24.270 --> 38:25.000
Hello, doctor.

38:25.000 --> 38:26.260
Did I ask you to come in?

38:26.790 --> 38:27.430
Get out.

38:27.630 --> 38:28.760
Come back in when I tell you to.

38:28.760 --> 38:29.110
Okay.

38:32.070 --> 38:33.440
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

38:35.340 --> 38:36.910
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

38:39.010 --> 38:41.260
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

38:44.120 --> 38:45.990
[Scan for cameras]

38:46.020 --> 38:46.600
[Loading]

38:46.620 --> 38:47.210
