39:19.320 --> 39:19.670
Hello?

39:19.390 --> 39:22.350
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

39:20.260 --> 39:21.390
Let me check.

39:23.430 --> 39:24.670
The sink is draining now.

39:23.890 --> 39:27.410
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

39:25.510 --> 39:26.360
Thank you.

39:40.810 --> 39:47.170
[July 18, 2019, Thursday]

39:52.000 --> 39:52.710
Honey,

39:52.990 --> 39:54.330
I need to go out now.

39:54.590 --> 39:57.590
Officer Li called me yesterday
and asked me to go meet him today.

39:57.590 --> 39:59.990
I guess there's progress on Leilei's case.

40:00.190 --> 40:00.940
Of course,

40:01.230 --> 40:03.060
it could also be about Ding Zhibo's case.

40:03.060 --> 40:05.120
I'll pick up groceries on my way home.

40:05.350 --> 40:10.070
[The Dark Romance]

40:26.690 --> 40:30.150
[Adult Psychiatric Clinic]

40:39.500 --> 40:44.320
[Harbor Island Edward Hospital]
[How to identify a mental health crisis]

40:47.150 --> 40:48.510
Zishan.

40:50.510 --> 40:51.420
Zishan.

40:54.030 --> 40:54.800
Zishan,

40:56.510 --> 40:58.590
what do you enjoy drawing most?

41:11.000 --> 41:12.530
Such a beautiful painting.

41:14.550 --> 41:16.210
This girl looks a lot like you.

41:19.070 --> 41:21.570
Who is that young man?

41:26.070 --> 41:27.280
I can't tell you.

41:29.360 --> 41:30.110
Why not?

41:34.230 --> 41:37.140
He said I couldn't tell anyone
about him yet,

41:38.460 --> 41:39.590
and that I had to wait

41:40.960 --> 41:42.680
till my mother gave approval.

41:44.840 --> 41:47.570
I understand
you and your mother were very close.

41:47.630 --> 41:49.660
You always listened to her.

41:50.320 --> 41:52.850
Did she not approve
of you two being together?

41:54.630 --> 41:56.250
Why did she not?

41:56.920 --> 41:58.360
Was it related to "that"?

42:13.510 --> 42:14.270
Zishan!
